'''卡倫·史考特'''（{{lang-en|'''Calum Scott'''}}，{{bd|1988年|10月12日|||catIdx=Scott, Calum}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/experimentUK/status/521352815982022656/photo/1 |publisher=The Experiment |title=Happy birthday to our frontman Calum have a great day mate |date=12 October 2014 |accessdate=2020-07-07 |archive-date=2016-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160418001033/https://twitter.com/experimentuk/status/521352815982022656/photo/1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>）是一名[[英國|英國]][[歌手|歌手]]和詞曲作者。2013年，他贏得了{{link-en|赫爾每日郵報|Hull Daily Mail}}舉行的才藝競賽<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hulldailymail.co.uk/Calum-Scott-talent-Winner-Star-Search-2013/story-19659977-detail/story.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706085842/http://www.hulldailymail.co.uk/Calum-Scott-talent-Winner-Star-Search-2013/story-19659977-detail/story.html |archive-date=2015-07-06 |title=Calum Scott talent: Winner of Star Search 2013 declared |work=Hull Daily Mail |date=15 August 2013 |accessdate=13 September 2018 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Winter |first1=Phil |title=Calum Scott releases debut album with intimate Hull gig in HMV |url=https://www.hulldailymail.co.uk/whats-on/music-nightlife/calum-scott-releases-debut-album-1324384 |website=HullLive |publisher=Hull Daily Mail |accessdate=14 September 2018 |date=10 March 2018 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808233057/https://www.hulldailymail.co.uk/whats-on/music-nightlife/calum-scott-releases-debut-album-1324384 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；2015年，他參加了著名的電視節目《[[英國達人|英國達人]]》後，享譽全球。隨後，他以單曲形式發行了[[蘿蘋|蘿蘋]]的熱門歌曲“Dancing On My Own”，在[[英國單曲排行榜|英國單曲排行榜]]上排名第二，並成為當年英國最暢銷的歌曲<ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/bpi_music/status/769187789543907329 |title=bpi music on Twitter: "Huge congrats to @calumscott! His single 'Dancing On My Own' has shot from Gold to Platinum! #bpiAwards" |publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]] |date=26 August 2016 |accessdate=4 November 2016 |archive-date=2022-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220129075737/https://twitter.com/bpi_music/status/769187789543907329 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年，他與[[利昂娜·刘易斯|利昂娜·刘易斯]]合作製作了單曲“{{link-en|You Are the Reason|You Are the Reason (Calum Scott song)}}”，這一首歌曲獲得極大成功<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/calumscott/status/1101212993457737734 |title=1,000,000,000 STREAMS OF 'YOU ARE THE REASON' |website=Twitter |accessdate=2020-07-07 |archive-date=2020-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200515175432/https://twitter.com/calumscott/status/1101212993457737734 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="allaccess">{{Cite web |url=https://www.allaccess.com/net-news/archive/story/178250/capitol-s-calum-scott-reaches-sales-streaming-mile |title=Capitol's Calum Scott Reaches Sales Milestones |website=All Access Music Group |access-date=2020-07-07 |archive-date=2019-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607202727/https://www.allaccess.com/net-news/archive/story/178250/capitol-s-calum-scott-reaches-sales-streaming-mile |dead-url=no }}</ref>，至2022年6月，該曲在[[Youtube|Youtube]]的觀看次數已超過8.5億次。

